<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Vulgar_Latin&amp;action=edit&amp;section=22" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://print.google.com/print?hl=en&amp;id=_OzEl6nLsGIC&amp;lpg=PR4&amp;pg=PR1&amp;printsec=4" class="external text" title="http://print.google.com/print?hl=en&amp;id=_OzEl6nLsGIC&amp;lpg=PR4&amp;pg=PR1&amp;printsec=4" rel="nofollow"><i>An Introduction to Vulgar Latin</i></a> by C.H. Grandgent</li>
<li><a href="http://www.orbilat.com/Languages/Latin_Medieval/Dag_Norberg/01.html" class="external text" title="http://www.orbilat.com/Languages/Latin_Medieval/Dag_Norberg/01.html" rel="nofollow"><i>Latin at the End of the Imperial Age</i></a> by Dag Norberg</li>
<li><a href="http://www.orbilat.com/index.html" class="external text" title="http://www.orbilat.com/index.html" rel="nofollow">Orbis Latinus</a>, a website about Latin and the Romance languages</li>
<li><a href="http://kaali.linguist.jussieu.fr/CGL/index.jsp" class="external text" title="http://kaali.linguist.jussieu.fr/CGL/index.jsp" rel="nofollow">Corpus Grammaticorum Latinorum: complete texts and full bibliography</a></li>
